Everything about docker-compose; available at https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/

docker-compose --help ~> Show help about docker-compose
docker-compose --version ~> Show version of docker-compose

docker-compose up ~> Create and start a container
docker-compose build ~> Realize only the build of the image of containers
docker-compose logs ~> Show logs of containers
docker-compose restart ~> Restart containers
docker-compose ps ~> Show all containers
docker-compose scale ~> Permits to increase a number of images containers
docker-compose start ~> Start a container
docker-compose stop ~> Stop a container
docker-compose down ~> Stop and remove all about containers